$ XAMPP installation directory: apache/conf/ssl.crt/server.crt

The server → development/security/cryptography/public-key/certificate.

This file is referenced from → development/web/service/stack/XAMPP/installation/directory/apache/conf/extra/httpd-ssl_conf[`apache/conf/extra/httpd-ssl.conf`] via the
`SSLCertificateFile` directive.

sa:

  This file can be created with with → development/web/service/stack/XAMPP/installation/directory/apache/makecert_bat[`apache/makecert.bat`]

  → development/web/service/stack/XAMPP/installation/directory/apache/conf/ssl_key/server_key[`conf/ssl.key/server.key`]
